  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "Qiao et al. [89] conducted experiments on two datasets: MS MARCO and ClueWeb09-B.",
    "The results showed that the three interaction-based BERT models delivered varying results on different datasets.",
    "Last-Int delivered better performance than the other two models on the MS MARCO dataset, and BERT Mult-Int delivered the worst performance in terms of MRR@10.",
    "However, BERT Mult-Int outperformed the other two methods on CluWeb09-B in terms of NDCG@20 and ERR@20.",
    "All the important models discussed above examine correlations between documents and a query to obtain a final, sorted list related to the query."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Qiao et al. [89] conducted experiments on two datasets: MS MARCO and ClueWeb09-B."
  ]
}